{#
  screenshot.njk
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Chapter-level screenshot panel. Sibling to chapter__content and
  chapter__mosaic — NOT a mosaic tile. Rendered by compiled-page.njk when
  chapter.screenshot is defined.

  Uses media.njk as a sub-include for the image (no figcaption inside).
  The __footer area is the bottom reserve below the image — holds future
  caption text and interactivity controls. Its height is derived (tile height
  minus top padding minus image height), never hardcoded.

  Visibility (opacity + transform) is owned by choreography.js via the same
  is-visible / is-exiting classes used on chapter__content.

  Usage (compiled-page.njk):
    {% set screenshotParams = chapter.screenshot %}
    {% include "components/screenshot.njk" %}

  YAML shape (chapter level in page.yml):
    screenshot:
      src: "/assets/images/impact-feed-v01.png"
      hasAlt: true
      alt: "Descriptive alt text"

  Required: src
  Optional: alt (required when hasAlt: true), hasAlt (default false)
  Future:   caption, controls
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#}

{% set sp = screenshotParams %}

{% if not sp %}
  <!-- SCREENSHOT_ERROR: screenshotParams not set -->
{% elif not sp.src %}
  <!-- SCREENSHOT_ERROR: screenshot.src is required -->
{% else %}

<div class="chapter__screenshot">
  {% set mediaParams = {
    src: sp.src,
    hasAlt: sp.hasAlt,
    alt: sp.alt,
    cssClass: "chapter__screenshot__img",
    sizes: "800px"
  } %}
  {% include "components/media.njk" %}
  <div class="chapter__screenshot__footer">
    {# caption and controls — future #}
  </div>
</div>

{% endif %}
